library(ggplot2)
pos <- cumsum(poll) - poll / 2
pos2 <- pos

poll_tbl <- data.frame(key = names(poll), value = poll, row.names = NULL)
ggplot(data = poll_tbl, mapping = aes(x = 2, y = value, fill = key)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
  geom_text(aes(y = pos2, label = poll), size = 7, colour = "white") +
  geom_text(aes(x = 2.8, 
                 y = pos2,
